{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.181532+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "**Flow:** `Record_Trigger_Opportunity_Approved` (created 2025-05-12)"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.183045+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "**What it does:**"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.184047+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "- Before-save trigger on Opportunity (create + update)"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.184550+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "- Entry criteria: StageName changed to or created as `Approved`"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.185553+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "- Action: Sets `Approved_Date__c = TODAY()` "}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.186057+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "**For HEAL-33072:**"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.186057+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "We can **extend this existing flow** instead of creating a new one. The current flow handles the Approved stage; we need to add logic for:"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.187568+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "- `Waiting For Approval` → sets `Submitted_Date__c = TODAY()`"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.187568+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "- `Rejected` → sets `Rejected_Date__c = TODAY()`"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.189083+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "**Recommendation:**"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.189083+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "Modify `Record_Trigger_Opportunity_Approved` to:"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.190597+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "1. Rename to broader label like `Record_Trigger_Opportunity_Stage_Changes`"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.190597+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "2. Add entry criteria branches for all three stages"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.192109+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "3. Each branch sets the appropriate date field"}
{"ts": "2026-05-14T20:01:43.192109+00:00", "run_key": "HEAL-33072", "kind": "line", "text": "This avoids creating redundant flows and keeps stage-tracking logic consolidated."}
